g:\quad {\mathbb R}^3\to{\mathbb R}^2,\qquad \tilde p\mapsto p\ ,
h:=g\circ f:\quad{\mathbb R}\to{\mathbb R}^2,\qquad \theta \mapsto g\bigl(f(\theta)\bigr) \ .
\theta\mapsto \tilde p(\theta)=\bigl(x(\theta),y(\theta),z(\theta)\bigr)\ ,
(x,y,z)\mapsto\cases{\xi:=x/z \cr \eta:=y/z \cr}\ .
\theta\mapsto\cases{\xi(\theta):=x(\theta)/z(\theta) \cr \eta(\theta):=y(\theta)/z(\theta) \cr}\ ,
